properties.areaDesc: Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI; Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI; Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 20 at 2:36PM CST until February 22 at 3:00AM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds increasing to 20 to 30 knots with a few
gale force gusts to 35 kts Friday afternoon. Waves will build to
4 to 7 feet Friday afternoon.

* WHERE...Lake Michigan nearshore waters from Rock Island Passage
to Sheboygan WI.

* WHEN...From 9 AM Friday to 3 AM CST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM FRIDAY TO 3 AM CST SATURDAY
